data.description: Beautiful 5 bedroom home with all newer appliances including stove, dishwasher and fridge. Master bedroom has his and her closet. Pellet stove to keep that electric bill down. Down stairs front room would be perfect for a theatre room. Laundry room has plenty of storage for all those extras. Backyard is fully fenced. New water heater, water softener and roof.
